<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Patagonia Equity · Simulador de Cartera</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:ital,wght@0,400;0,500;0,600;0,700;1,400&family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
:root{
  --navy:#1a3a6a;--navy2:#0f2348;--navy3:#081628;
  --gold:#c3a23c;--gold2:#e8c96a;--gold-bg:#fdf8ec;
  --bg:#f7f5f0;--white:#fff;
  --text:#1e1c18;--mid:#6b6760;--light:#b0aca4;--border:#e0dcd6;
  --green:#186e37;--red:#b9261a;--teal:#126973;
  --shadow:0 4px 32px rgba(26,58,106,.10);
}
*,*::before,*::after{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box;}
html{font-size:16px;}
body{font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif;background:var(--bg);color:var(--text);min-height:100vh;overflow-x:hidden;}
body::after{content:'';position:fixed;inset:0;pointer-events:none;z-index:0;
  background:radial-gradient(ellipse 70% 50% at 5% 15%,rgba(195,162,60,.05) 0%,transparent 55%),
             radial-gradient(ellipse 50% 70% at 95% 85%,rgba(26,58,106,.06) 0%,transparent 55%);}

/* HEADER */
.header{position:fixed;top:0;left:0;right:0;z-index:200;height:64px;
  background:rgba(255,255,255,.95);backdrop-filter:blur(16px);
  border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);box-shadow:0 1px 20px rgba(26,58,106,.07);
  display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;padding:0 52px;}
.header::after{content:'';position:absolute;bottom:0;left:0;right:0;height:3px;
  background:linear-gradient(90deg,var(--navy) 0%,var(--gold) 50%,var(--navy) 100%);}
.logo{font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-size:21px;font-weight:600;color:var(--navy);}
.logo em{color:var(--gold);font-style:normal;}
.logo-sub{font-size:10px;color:var(--light);letter-spacing:.1em;text-transform:uppercase;margin-top:1px;}
.hpill{font-size:11px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:.07em;text-transform:uppercase;
  color:var(--gold);background:var(--navy);padding:5px 16px;border-radius:20px;}

/* PROGRESS */
.pbar{position:fixed;top:64px;left:0;right:0;z-index:190;background:var(--white);
  border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);padding:14px 52px 24px;}
.ptrack{max-width:620px;margin:0 auto;display:flex;align-items:center;}
.pstep{display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;flex:1;position:relative;}
.pdot{width:28px;height:28px;border-radius:50%;border:2px solid var(--border);
  background:var(--white);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;
  font-size:10px;font-weight:600;color:var(--light);
  transition:all .35s cubic-bezier(.4,0,.2,1);position:relative;z-index:2;}
.pdot.active{border-color:var(--gold);background:var(--gold);color:var(--navy2);
  transform:scale(1.2);box-shadow:0 0 0 5px rgba(195,162,60,.18);}
.pdot.done{border-color:var(--green);background:var(--green);color:var(--white);}
.pdot.done .pn{display:none;}
.pdot.done::before{content:'✓';font-size:12px;}
.plbl{position:absolute;top:34px;font-size:8.5px;font-weight:500;color:var(--light);
  text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.05em;white-space:nowrap;}
.pdot.active .plbl{color:var(--navy);font-weight:600;}
.pdot.done .plbl{color:var(--green);}
.pline{flex:1;height:2px;background:var(--border);
  transition:background .4s ease;margin-top:-28px;position:relative;z-index:1;}
.pline.done{background:var(--green);}

/* MAIN */
.main{min-height:100vh;padding:154px 52px 80px;max-width:860px;margin:0 auto;position:relative;z-index:1;}
.screen{display:none;}
.screen.active{display:block;animation:slideUp .42s cubic-bezier(.4,0,.2,1);}
@keyframes slideUp{from{opacity:0;transform:translateY(22px)}to{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0)}}

/* QUESTION */
.eyebrow{font-size:11px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:.16em;text-transform:uppercase;
  color:var(--gold);margin-bottom:10px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;}
.eyebrow::before{content:'';display:block;width:24px;height:2px;background:var(--gold);}
.qtitle{font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-size:40px;line-height:1.1;font-weight:600;
  color:var(--navy);margin-bottom:10px;}
.qhint{font-size:14px;color:var(--mid);line-height:1.65;margin-bottom:34px;max-width:580px;}

/* OPTIONS */
.opts{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:11px;}
.opt{background:var(--white);border:2px solid var(--border);border-radius:14px;
  padding:20px 24px;cursor:pointer;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:16px;
  transition:all .22s ease;position:relative;overflow:hidden;}
.opt::before{content:'';position:absolute;left:0;top:0;bottom:0;width:0;background:var(--navy);transition:width .22s;}
.opt:hover{border-color:var(--gold);box-shadow:var(--shadow);transform:translateX(3px);}
.opt:hover::before{width:4px;background:var(--gold);}
.opt.sel{border-color:var(--navy);background:rgba(26,58,106,.03);transform:translateX(4px);}
.opt.sel::before{width:5px;}
.oicon{font-size:26px;width:48px;height:48px;flex-shrink:0;background:var(--bg);
  border-radius:11px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;}
.opt.sel .oicon{background:rgba(26,58,106,.08);}
.obody{flex:1;}
.otitle{font-size:15px;font-weight:600;color:var(--text);margin-bottom:2px;}
.odesc{font-size:12.5px;color:var(--mid);line-height:1.5;}
.oradio{width:20px;height:20px;border-radius:50%;border:2px solid var(--border);
  flex-shrink:0;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;transition:all .2s;}
.opt.sel .oradio{background:var(--navy);border-color:var(--navy);}
.opt.sel .oradio::after{content:'';display:block;width:7px;height:7px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--white);}

/* ── TRAMOS SLIDER ── */
.tramos-wrap{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:18px;margin-bottom:8px;}
.tramo{background:var(--white);border:2px solid var(--border);border-radius:14px;padding:20px 24px;}
.tramo-top{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;margin-bottom:14px;}
.tramo-left{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;}
.tramo-icon{font-size:24px;width:44px;height:44px;border-radius:10px;
  display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex-shrink:0;}
.tramo-name{font-size:15px;font-weight:600;color:var(--text);}
.tramo-sub{font-size:12px;color:var(--mid);margin-top:2px;}
.tramo-pct{font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-size:36px;font-weight:700;
  color:var(--navy);min-width:68px;text-align:right;line-height:1;}
.tramo-slider{-webkit-appearance:none;appearance:none;width:100%;height:6px;
  border-radius:3px;outline:none;cursor:pointer;
  background:linear-gradient(to right,var(--c,var(--navy)) 0%,var(--c,var(--navy)) var(--p,33%),#e0dcd6 var(--p,33%));
  transition:background .15s;}
.tramo-slider::-webkit-slider-thumb{-webkit-appearance:none;width:22px;height:22px;
  border-radius:50%;background:var(--navy);border:3px solid var(--white);
  box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(26,58,106,.28);cursor:pointer;}
.tramo-bar-labels{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;font-size:10px;color:var(--light);margin-top:6px;}

/* Total indicator */
.total-box{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;
  background:var(--gold-bg);border:1.5px solid var(--gold);border-radius:10px;
  padding:12px 18px;margin-top:8px;}
.total-label{font-size:13px;color:#7a6020;font-weight:500;}
.total-val{font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-size:28px;font-weight:700;}
.total-val.ok{color:var(--green);}
.total-val.bad{color:var(--red);}
.total-hint{font-size:11px;color:var(--mid);margin-top:4px;}

/* ── SOFISTICACIÓN GRID ── */
.sofis-wrap{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:16px;margin-bottom:8px;}
.sofis-col{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:10px;}
.sofis-label{font-size:11px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:.1em;text-transform:uppercase;
  color:var(--mid);margin-bottom:4px;padding-left:4px;}
.sofis-opt{background:var(--white);border:2px solid var(--border);border-radius:12px;
  padding:16px 18px;cursor:pointer;transition:all .2s;position:relative;overflow:hidden;}
.sofis-opt::before{content:'';position:absolute;left:0;top:0;bottom:0;width:0;background:var(--navy);transition:width .2s;}
.sofis-opt:hover{border-color:var(--gold);box-shadow:var(--shadow);}
.sofis-opt:hover::before{width:4px;background:var(--gold);}
.sofis-opt.sel{border-color:var(--navy);background:rgba(26,58,106,.03);}
.sofis-opt.sel::before{width:4px;}
.sofis-icon{font-size:22px;margin-bottom:6px;}
.sofis-title{font-size:14px;font-weight:600;color:var(--text);margin-bottom:3px;}
.sofis-desc{font-size:11.5px;color:var(--mid);line-height:1.45;}
.sofis-divider{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;padding-top:28px;}
.sofis-divider-line{width:1px;height:100%;background:var(--border);}
.sofis-vs{font-size:12px;font-weight:600;color:var(--light);letter-spacing:.08em;
  text-transform:uppercase;writing-mode:vertical-rl;padding:12px 0;}

/* Perfil badge resultado sofis */
.sofis-result{margin-top:16px;padding:14px 18px;border-radius:10px;
  background:var(--navy);color:var(--white);font-size:13px;
  display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;display:none;}
.sofis-result.show{display:flex;}
.sofis-result-badge{font-size:20px;}
.sofis-result-text{line-height:1.4;}
.sofis-result-text strong{color:var(--gold2);display:block;}

/* CAPITAL */
.capcard{background:var(--white);border:2px solid var(--border);border-radius:16px;padding:30px 34px;box-shadow:var(--shadow);}
.capamt{font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-size:50px;font-weight:700;color:var(--navy);line-height:1;margin-bottom:4px;}
.capcur{font-size:24px;color:var(--gold);margin-right:6px;}
.capusd{font-size:13px;color:var(--mid);margin-bottom:26px;padding:5px 12px;background:var(--gold-bg);border-radius:6px;display:inline-block;border-left:3px solid var(--gold);}
input.caprange{width:100%;height:5px;-webkit-appearance:none;appearance:none;
  background:linear-gradient(to right,var(--navy) 0%,var(--navy) var(--pct,18%),var(--border) var(--pct,18%));
  border-radius:3px;outline:none;cursor:pointer;margin-bottom:10px;}
input.caprange::-webkit-slider-thumb{-webkit-appearance:none;width:22px;height:22px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--navy);border:3px solid var(--white);box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(26,58,106,.28);}
.rticks{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;font-size:10px;color:var(--light);margin-bottom:18px;}
.capquick{display:flex;gap:8px;flex-wrap:wrap;}
.qbtn{padding:5px 13px;border-radius:20px;font-size:12px;font-weight:500;border:1.5px solid var(--border);background:var(--bg);color:var(--mid);cursor:pointer;transition:all .18s;font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif;}
.qbtn:hover{border-color:var(--gold);color:var(--navy);}
.qbtn.active{background:var(--navy);color:var(--gold);border-color:var(--navy);}

/* NAV */
.nav{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;margin-top:40px;}
.btn{font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif;font-size:15px;font-weight:600;border:none;cursor:pointer;border-radius:10px;transition:all .22s ease;padding:13px 30px;}
.bbk{background:transparent;color:var(--mid);border:2px solid var(--border);}
.bbk:hover{border-color:var(--navy);color:var(--navy);}
.bnx{background:var(--navy);color:var(--gold);padding:13px 42px;box-shadow:0 4px 18px rgba(26,58,106,.22);}
.bnx:hover{background:var(--navy2);transform:translateY(-2px);}
.bnx:disabled{background:var(--border);color:var(--light);cursor:not-allowed;transform:none;box-shadow:none;}
.bgen{background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--gold) 0%,#9e7818 100%);color:var(--navy2);padding:15px 50px;font-size:16px;box-shadow:0 6px 28px rgba(195,162,60,.38);}
.bgen:hover{transform:translateY(-3px);box-shadow:0 12px 36px rgba(195,162,60,.46);}

/* RESULT */
.rhero{border-radius:18px;padding:36px 42px;margin-bottom:22px;
  background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--navy) 0%,var(--navy2) 60%,var(--navy3) 100%);
  position:relative;overflow:hidden;}
.rhero::before{content:'';position:absolute;right:-60px;top:-60px;width:260px;height:260px;border-radius:50%;background:radial-gradient(circle,rgba(195,162,60,.12) 0%,transparent 70%);}
.rperfil{font-size:11px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:.14em;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(195,162,60,.7);margin-bottom:8px;}
.rtitle{font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-size:36px;font-weight:700;color:var(--white);margin-bottom:6px;}
.rdesc{font-size:13.5px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.65);margin-bottom:20px;line-height:1.6;max-width:480px;}
.rchips{display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:8px;}
.chip{padding:5px 13px;border-radius:20px;font-size:11px;font-weight:500;background:rgba(195,162,60,.15);color:var(--gold2);border:1px solid rgba(195,162,60,.28);}

/* Tramos result */
.tramos-result{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:10px;margin-bottom:20px;}
.tr-card{background:var(--white);border-radius:11px;padding:14px 16px;border:1.5px solid var(--border);text-align:center;}
.tr-pct{font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-size:28px;font-weight:700;}
.tr-name{font-size:10px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.07em;color:var(--light);margin-top:2px;}

.srow{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:11px;margin-bottom:22px;}
.scard{background:var(--white);border-radius:12px;padding:16px 20px;border:1.5px solid var(--border);text-align:center;}
.sval{font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-size:24px;font-weight:700;color:var(--navy);}
.slbl{font-size:10px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.08em;color:var(--light);margin-top:2px;}

.agrid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:13px;margin-bottom:22px;}
.acard{background:var(--white);border-radius:13px;border:1.5px solid var(--border);padding:18px 20px;position:relative;overflow:hidden;box-shadow:0 2px 10px rgba(0,0,0,.04);transition:all .2s;}
.acard:hover{transform:translateY(-3px);box-shadow:var(--shadow);}
.astripe{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;bottom:0;width:5px;}
.atop{display:flex;align-items:flex-start;justify-content:space-between;margin-bottom:12px;}
.aicon{font-size:20px;padding-left:10px;}
.aname{font-size:12.5px;font-weight:600;color:var(--text);margin-top:3px;padding-left:10px;}
.aname-tech{font-size:10px;color:var(--light);padding-left:10px;margin-top:1px;font-style:italic;}
.apct{font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-size:36px;font-weight:700;line-height:1;}
.abarbg{height:5px;background:var(--border);border-radius:3px;margin-bottom:7px;}
.abar{height:100%;border-radius:3px;animation:barIn 1.1s cubic-bezier(.4,0,.2,1) forwards;}
@keyframes barIn{from{width:0}}
.amonto{font-size:11px;color:var(--mid);padding-left:10px;}
.awhy{font-size:10.5px;color:var(--mid);padding-left:10px;margin-top:4px;line-height:1.45;font-style:italic;}

.exclbox{background:#fff5f5;border-radius:10px;padding:13px 17px;border-left:4px solid var(--red);margin-bottom:14px;font-size:12.5px;color:#7a1a1a;line-height:1.6;}
.rulesbox{background:var(--gold-bg);border-radius:12px;padding:16px 20px;border-left:4px solid var(--gold);margin-bottom:18px;font-size:12.5px;color:#7a6020;line-height:1.9;}
.rulesbox strong{display:block;margin-bottom:7px;color:var(--navy);font-size:13.5px;}
.actrow{display:flex;gap:10px;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-top:4px;}
.bprint{background:transparent;color:var(--navy);border:2px solid var(--navy);padding:10px 24px;font-size:13px;border-radius:8px;cursor:pointer;font-weight:600;transition:all .2s;font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif;}
.bprint:hover{background:var(--navy);color:var(--gold);}
.breset{background:transparent;color:var(--mid);border:2px solid var(--border);padding:10px 24px;font-size:13px;border-radius:8px;cursor:pointer;font-weight:500;transition:all .2s;font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif;}
.breset:hover{border-color:var(--navy);color:var(--navy);}
.discl{font-size:11px;color:var(--light);text-align:center;border-top:1px solid var(--border);padding-top:18px;margin-top:22px;line-height:1.8;}

.icard{background:var(--white);border-radius:12px;padding:20px 16px;border:1.5px solid var(--border);text-align:center;}

/* carry badge */
.carry-badge{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;background:rgba(26,58,106,.08);
  border:1px solid rgba(26,58,106,.2);border-radius:20px;padding:4px 12px;
  font-size:11px;color:var(--navy);font-weight:500;margin-top:8px;}

@media(max-width:640px){
  .header{padding:0 20px;}.pbar{padding:12px 20px 24px;}.main{padding:152px 20px 60px;}
  .qtitle{font-size:28px;}.agrid{grid-template-columns:1fr;}.srow{grid-template-columns:1fr;}
  .sofis-wrap{grid-template-columns:1fr;}.tramos-result{grid-template-columns:1fr;}
  .capamt{font-size:36px;}.rtitle{font-size:26px;}
}
/* PRÓXIMO PASO */
.proximos{background:var(--navy);border-radius:16px;padding:28px 32px;margin-bottom:22px;}
.proximos-title{font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-size:22px;font-weight:600;color:var(--white);margin-bottom:10px;}
.proximos-desc{font-size:13.5px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.7);line-height:1.6;margin-bottom:20px;}
.proximos-actions{display:flex;gap:12px;flex-wrap:wrap;}
.proximos-btn{text-decoration:none;display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;}
.proximos-email{font-size:12.5px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.55);margin-top:14px;}
.proximos-email strong{color:var(--gold2);}
@media print{.proximos{background:var(--navy)!important;-webkit-print-color-adjust:exact;print-color-adjust:exact;page-break-inside:avoid;}}

</style>
</head>
<body>

<header class="header">
  <div><div class="logo">Patagonia <em>Equity</em></div><div class="logo-sub">Asesoramiento Financiero</div></div>
  <div class="hpill">Simulador de Cartera</div>
</header>
<div class="pbar"><div class="ptrack" id="PT"></div></div>

<main class="main">

<!-- INTRO -->
<div class="screen active" id="s0">
  <div class="eyebrow">Bienvenido</div>
  <div class="qtitle">Encontrá la cartera que se adapta a vos</div>
  <div class="qhint">7 preguntas sobre tu situación real — sin tecnicismos. El sistema determina qué instrumentos son adecuados para tu perfil y construye la asignación automáticamente.</div>
  <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:14px;margin-bottom:42px">
    <div class="icard"><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:10px">⏱</div><div style="font-size:13px;font-weight:600;color:var(--navy);margin-bottom:4px">2 minutos</div><div style="font-size:12px;color:var(--mid)">7 preguntas simples</div></div>
    <div class="icard"><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:10px">🎯</div><div style="font-size:13px;font-weight:600;color:var(--navy);margin-bottom:4px">Sin sesgos</div><div style="font-size:12px;color:var(--mid)">El sistema elige por vos</div></div>
    <div class="icard"><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:10px">📊</div><div style="font-size:13px;font-weight:600;color:var(--navy);margin-bottom:4px">Cartera real</div><div style="font-size:12px;color:var(--mid)">Con pesos sugeridos</div></div>
  </div>
  <div style="background:#fdf8ec;border:1.5px solid #c3a23c;border-radius:12px;padding:16px 20px;margin-bottom:28px;display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:12px;">
    <span style="font-size:20px;flex-shrink:0">🔍</span>
    <div>
      <div style="font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-size:15px;font-weight:600;color:#1a3a6a;margin-bottom:4px;">Esto es una simulación</div>
      <div style="font-size:13px;color:#6b6760;line-height:1.6;">Este simulador muestra cómo podría verse un modelo de inversión según tu perfil. <strong style="color:#1a3a6a;">No constituye una recomendación de inversión.</strong> Los resultados son orientativos y no reemplazan el asesoramiento profesional.</div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="nav" style="justify-content:flex-end"><button class="btn bnx" onclick="go(1)">Comenzar →</button></div>
</div>

<!-- P1: COMPOSICION DEL CAPITAL -->
<div class="screen" id="s1">
  <div class="eyebrow">Pregunta 1 de 7</div>
  <div class="qtitle">¿Cómo está compuesto este capital?</div>
  <div class="qhint">Distribuí el 100% entre los tres tipos de fondos. Esto define la estrategia base antes de cualquier otra consideración.</div>

  <div class="tramos-wrap">
    <!-- LIQUIDO -->
    <div class="tramo">
